<!DOCTYPE html>

	<head>
		<title>Coloc'all - Payback email</title>
		<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
	</head>


	<body>
        <div style="padding: 5px;border: 1px solid #d5d5d5;background: #fafafa;background-image: -webkit-linear-gradient(top, #fcfcfc, #f0f0f0);background-image: -moz-linear-gradient(top, #fcfcfc, #f0f0f0);background-image: -o-linear-gradient(top, #fcfcfc, #f0f0f0);background-image: linear-gradient(to bottom, #fcfcfc, #f0f0f0);-webkit-box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 1px #fafafa;box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 1px #fafafa;box-shadow: 0px 1px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);">
            <a href="http://www.colocall.co"><img src="http://www.colocall.co/web/img/logo.png" height="40px"; alt="logo Coloc'all"></a>
        </div>

		<p>Hello <b>{{ recipient.nickname }},</b></p>
		<p>Your flatmate {{ payback.author.nickname }} requested a payback on <a href="http://www.colocall.co">Coloc'all</a>. <b>All balances have been set to 0</b> and past expenses have been archived and locked</p>

		<p>To see what you owe/are own, you should refer to the following payments:</p>

		<div style="margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; width: 500px; border: solid 1px grey; border-radius: 10px;"> 
            <div style="text-align: center; color: grey; border-bottom: solid 1px grey">
                <h3>Payments</h3>
            </div>                    
            <div>
                <table>
                    <thead>
                        <tr>
                            <th style="width: 200px;">Who ?</th>
                            <th style="width: 200px;">To</th>
                            <th style="width: 200px;">Whom ?</th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody style="border: solid 1px; width: 100%;">                          
                        {% for payment in payback.paymentsArray %}
                            <tr style="text-align: center; border: solid 1px; width: 100%;">
                                <td>
                                    <div>
                                        <p>{{ payment[0] }}</p> 
                                    </div>
                                </td>
                                <td>
                                    <div style="color: rgb(0, 102, 0);font-weight: bold;text-align: center;">
                                        <p> {{ payment[1] }}{{ app.user.coloc.currency.symbol }}</p>
                                    </div>
                                </td>
                                <td>
                                    <div>
                                        <p>{{ payment[2] }}</p> 
                                    </div>                                
                                </td>
                            </tr>
                        {% endfor %}
                    </tbody>
                </table>  
            </div>
        </div>

        <p>Thank you for using Coloc'all,</p>
        <p>The team</p>

	</body>
</html>